==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Browbeating
<hw>Brow"beat`ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of bearing down,
abashing, or disconcerting, with stern looks, supercilious manners, or
confident assertions.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The imperious <qex>browbeatings</qex> and scorn of great men.</q>
<rj><qau>L'Estrange.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Browbound</ent>⟦br⟧
